{"id":407797,"name":null,"username":"bloodhound","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/bloodhound/{size}/22_2.png","created_at":"2022-06-16T13:17:29.000Z","cooked":"<p>Hey, given that Mills hasnt updated us with his progress in the old thread you also replied to, it looks like he didnt get around to writing an exporter, and I guess neither did anyone else.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"magicse\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"15799\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"//forum.magicball.net/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/d07c76/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> magicse:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Hi, I saw  LBA 2 island viewer. But it has no export. How can I export the island as a 3d model? Or tell me where I can find a description of the island format and objects on it.<br>\n<img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/angry.png?v=12\" title=\":angry:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom only-emoji\" alt=\":angry:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>The updated link that Lupin mentioned in that thread would be <a href=\"http://lbafileinfo.kaziq.net/index.php?title=LBA2:Citabau.ile\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">LBA2:Citabau.ile - LBA File Information</a><br>\nAnd the source code that xesf mentioned seems to now be at <a href=\"https://github.com/LBALab/lba2remake/tree/master/src/game/scenery/island\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">lba2remake/src/game/scenery/island at master  LBALab/lba2remake  GitHub</a></p>\n<p>Well then, good luck, and keep us up to date with your progress <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/wink.png?v=12\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":wink:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>","post_number":2,"post_type":1,"posts_count":19,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T20:06:09.164Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":2,"reads":12,"readers_count":11,"score":17.4,"yours":false,"topic_id":15799,"topic_slug":"lba-2-island-models-export","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":"Hgsippe","title_is_group":false,"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Hey, given that Mills hasn't updated us with his progress in the old thread you also replied to, it looks like he didn't get around to writing an exporter, and I guess neither did anyone else.\n\n\n[quote=\"magicse,post:1,topic:15799\"]\nHi, I saw  LBA 2 island viewer. But it has no export. How can I export the island as a 3d model? Or tell me where I can find a description of the island format and objects on it.\n:hmpf:\n[/quote]\n\nThe updated link that Lupin mentioned in that thread would be http://lbafileinfo.kaziq.net/index.php?title=LBA2:Citabau.ile\nAnd the source code that xesf mentioned seems to now be at https://github.com/LBALab/lba2remake/tree/master/src/game/scenery/island\n\nWell then, good luck, and keep us up to date with your progress ;)","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":34,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba-2-island-models-export/15799/2","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
