{"id":407803,"name":null,"username":"bloodhound","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/bloodhound/{size}/22_2.png","created_at":"2022-06-17T17:54:27.000Z","cooked":"<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"magicse\" data-post=\"4\" data-topic=\"15799\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"//forum.magicball.net/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/d07c76/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> magicse:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>some test</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Yeah would be cool to remake the islands in that style! (Though its still a bit too regular in some places in terms of color and shape). What did you use to create this?</p>\n<p>Its a pity creating an island exporter is so hard. I think for a programmer not familiar with this it would take at least a month, to learn about the export format, how to stitch the individual parts together into an island model, how to add textures and colors, etc.</p>","post_number":6,"post_type":1,"posts_count":19,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T20:06:09.220Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":4,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":2,"reads":8,"readers_count":7,"score":16.6,"yours":false,"topic_id":15799,"topic_slug":"lba-2-island-models-export","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":"Hgsippe","title_is_group":false,"bookmarked":false,"raw":"\n[quote=\"magicse,post:4,topic:15799\"]\nsome test\n[/quote]\n\nYeah would be cool to remake the islands in that style! (Though it's still a bit too regular in some places in terms of color and shape). What did you use to create this?\n\nIt's a pity creating an island exporter is so hard. I think for a programmer not familiar with this it would take at least a month, to learn about the export format, how to stitch the individual parts together into an island model, how to add textures and colors, etc.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":34,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba-2-island-models-export/15799/6","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
