{"id":407818,"name":null,"username":"magicse","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/d07c76/{size}.png","created_at":"2022-06-23T08:25:44.000Z","cooked":"<aside class=\"quote no-group\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Without the houses I didnt even recognize your screenshot as Citadel Island :D</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p><img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=12\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom only-emoji\" alt=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>For exposure I think if your tool is open source you can add it to <a href=\"https://github.com/LBALab/\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">LBA Lab  GitHub</a>, or if its not, then you could ask elmuerte to add it to the MBNs download section.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Still in the coding process. There are bugs and some fixes.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Of course it would be great if it converted all the island models, not just Citadel Island.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Yes, of course, I will complete the possibility of exporting any islands.</p>\n<p>Now Im posting the export of the citadel island with the correct heights.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fex.net/ru/s/l5epydc\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://fex.net/ru/s/l5epydc</a></p>","post_number":12,"post_type":1,"posts_count":19,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T19:13:24.887Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":11,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":3,"reads":10,"readers_count":9,"score":17.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":15799,"topic_slug":"lba-2-island-models-export","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":